# Schema / migrations (production Supabase)

**After pushing, apply any new migration files to production Supabase immediately. Do not consider the task done until the migration is confirmed applied.**

Use `npx supabase db push`, the Supabase Dashboard SQL editor (exact migration file contents), or your operator process — then confirm in hosted migration history / `migration list`. See [`docs/SUPABASE_MIGRATIONS.md`](docs/SUPABASE_MIGRATIONS.md).
